<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
		<title></title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="layui.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="font-awesome.min.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
		<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.min.js"></script>
		<script src="echarts.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>灯光控制器</h1>
		<h2>当前模式</h2>
		<div id="mode1" onclick="change2()" style="color: #FFFFFF;background: #1E9FFF;">自动模式</div>
		<div id="mode2" onclick="change1()">手动模式</div>
		<div id="div" class="layui-container" style="border:none">
			<div class="layui-row">
				<div id="light">
					<strong style="font-size:20px;">光强度:&ensp;</strong>
					<i id="light1"><%=data.light%></i><i>Lux</i><br>
					灯光指令&ensp;<i id="order" style="color:red;"><%=data.switch%></i><br>
					<i>自动模式下指令无效,，手动模式下开关不受光照强度限制</i><br>
					<i>ps：灯光控制规则：强度≦50Lux 时，自动打开路灯：光强度≧200Lux 时，自动关闭路灯</i>
				</div>
				<div id="open">
					<h3 id="title"></h3>
					<label class="switch">
					  <input id="select" type="checkbox" name="open">
					  <div class="slider round"></div>
					</label>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<script src="show.js" type="text/javascript" ></script>
	</body>
</html>
